INSERT INTO public.volunteer VALUES (112, 'I live in Wilmersdorf that is why I only selected 2 options but I can also do other locations if needed', 'My name is Sevval and I am a 27 year-old Turkish woman. I moved to Berlin in 2021 for my masters (in competition law) at FU and I have been working in the field as a consultant for over a year. Before that, I was working at a law firm in Istanbul. I always had a special interest in psychology and I have always got along with kids. I worked as a volunteer teacher in Ukaine in 2017 for over a month. When I saw this advert, I felt very excited and I would love to be a part of this with my whole heart. My German skills are around B1.2-B2  -Vostel
